  "description": "A brain exercising game in the style of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Brain+Age\">Brain Age</a> that was developed by Dr. Makoto Shichida of Newport University of Japan that was developed with another Brain Boost game, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/brain-boost-beta-wave\">Beta Wave</a>, which are both designed to stimulate the players right side of their brain.<br><br>There are two games to choose from: <i>Training</i> and </i>Challenge</i> with five different remembering games to choose from: Colors, Numbers, Faces, Images and Events from a multiple choice of four answers.  Players are awarded points for correct answers and bonus points for answering them before a time limit.<br><br>Each game contains four stages with 20 problems a piece, advancing through the levels by completing a certain percentage of answers (50% in Training mode and 60% in Challenge mode) and keep track their development throughout the game.",
